@startuml
actor Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "customer-service" as CustomerService
participant "mobile-service" as MobileService
database "PostgreSQL Mobile DB" as MobileDB

Customer -> Gateway: GET /api/customers/mobiles/search/
Gateway -> CustomerService: GET /customers/mobiles/search/
CustomerService -> CustomerService: Validate JWT customer
CustomerService -> MobileService: GET /mobiles/search/
MobileService -> MobileDB: Filter by q/brand/price
MobileDB --> MobileService: Search result
MobileService --> CustomerService: Result set
CustomerService --> Gateway: Response JSON
Gateway --> Customer: Search result
@enduml
